original_title: C-SPAN StudentCam: FEMA's Impact on Our Lives in SWLA
overview: As part of the 2022 C-SPAN StudentCam Student Documentary Competition, Television Production students Jason Boudreaux, Jaleaha Joseph and Shontenaisha Manuel explore FEMA's impact on their lives in Southwest Louisiana.
title: C-SPAN StudentCam: FEMA's Impact on Our Lives in SWLA
